Mukhtar Yahia Naji AL WARAFI, petitioner,
v.
Barack H. OBAMA, President of the United States. No. 13-768. Supreme Court of the United States May 5, 2014. Case below, 716 F.3d 627 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.
